dy\n* Vivekananda Tamil Vidyalayam\n* [[Wariyapola Sri Sumangala college|Wariyapola Sri Sumangala College, Kandy]]\n* Wattappola Maha Vidyalaya\n* [[Wattegama Central College]]\n* Zahira Boys College, Katugasthota\n* Yahalatenne  Muslim Maha Vidyalaya, Kandy\n*Udadumbara secondary school ,Udadumbara\n\n===Private schools===\n* [[St. Anthony's College, Kandy]]\n* [[Trinity College, Kandy]]\n* St. Benedict's College Kandy\n* [[Hillwood College]], Kandy\n* Asoka College, Kandy\n* Good Shepherd Convent, Kandy\n* Sri Chandananda Buddhist College, Kandy\n* Mowbray College, Kandy\n* Sinhala Buddhist College, Matale\n* Sussex College, Kandy\n\n===International schools===  \n* Harvard Medha International School, Haragama, Kandy\n* [[\u00c9cole internationale Kandy|\u00c9cole internationale]], Kandy\n* [[Gateway College, Sri Lanka|Gateway College]], Kandy (formally Kandy International School)\n* [[Leeds International School Nawalapitiya]]\n* [[Lexicon International School]], Kandy\n* Colombo International School, Kandy\n* Dhurham College Galhinna\n* Gampola International School Gampola\n* Hill Country International School, Kandy\n* [http://kgsch.com/ Kandy Grammar School, Kandy]\n* Kingston English School, Kandy\n* Savihx College, Nawalapitiya\n* Netherfield International School, Kandy\n* Niswan Model School, Ambathanne\n* Rightway International School Kandy\n* Irish International School\n* Sherwood Girls College\n* [http://springfield.lk/ Springfield International School, Kandy]\n* Wesswood International Boys' College Katugastota\n* Yaqeen Model School, Ambathanne\n* Stamford College, Kandy\n*Oxford college, Nawalapitiya\n\n==Matale District==\n\n===Rattota===\n<br />\n====Rattota division====\n\n* Al Furkhan Muslim M.V. Galewela\n* Aluthwewa K.V. Bambaragaswewa\n* ANDAGALA P.S.BAMBARAGASWEWA\n* BAMBAWA P.S.GALEWELA\n* BELIGAMUWA K.V.BELIGAMUWA\n* BULANAWEWA P.S.\tDEWAHUWA\n* DAMUNUMULLA K.V.DAMUNUMULLA\n* DANDUBENDIRUPPA K.V.DEWAHUWA\n* DEWAHUWA MUS M.V.DEWAHUWA\n* DEWAHUWA